com.itko.lisaint.wshandler

Class JaxRpcHandler

  • java.lang.Object
    • javax.xml.rpc.handler.GenericHandler
      • com.itko.lisaint.wshandler.JaxRpcHandler
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    javax.xml.rpc.handler.Handler
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    CapeClearInterceptor, Wls81JaxRpcHandler

    public class JaxRpcHandler
extends javax.xml.rpc.handler.GenericHandler
    A JAX-RPC MessageHandler to inject LISA integration tags into the response SOAP header. This can be configured on a per-service basis or globally - each app server / WS stack has a different way of doing so. Consult the LISA developer guide or contact support@itko.com for details.
